'''Mason Givesoft''' (1918 - 2001) was an American trucker and racing enthusiast. He was the father of race car driver [[Dene Givesoft (V2)|Dene Givesoft]]. A big rig expert, he would often partake in truck racing, which influenced his son's career. 

